headline: GTA Online
subtitle: Discounts
content:
There are a range of discounts on offer throughout Los Santos this week that benefit white-collar and blue-collar criminals alike, namely:

- 40% off MC Clubhouses
- 40% off Executive Offices
- 40% off Biker Businesses
- 30% off Executive Office Customizations

And more! Check out the Rockstar Newswire for more details.
